com.vmware.vcenter.vm

Class GuestOS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<GuestOS>
      • com.vmware.vcenter.vm.GuestOS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class GuestOS
extends ApiEnumeration<GuestOS>
    The GuestOS enumeration class defines the valid guest operating system types used for configuring a virtual machine.

    See enumerated types description.

    See Also:
